{"tid":542482,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有咩方法可以完全冇哂面油","createTime":"2018-01-27T13:36:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-28T10:59:54.000Z","uid":15501,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c899d6183d0cbe9a8a6be753b6eb61884ee5a8c8","tid":542482,"uid":15501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T13:36:57.000Z","msg":"之生面油多又成日生暗瘡<br />\n後來食左一個療程a酸<br />\n食緊個時完全冇哂面油感覺好正<br />\n但停左藥到而家唔夠一個月<br />\nT字位開始有返油出，雖則冇以前咁多<br />\n但我完全唔鐘意有面油既感覺<br />\n想問下有冇咩方法可以完全冇油出<br />\n聽講有人會keep住食低濟量a酸<br />\n面部既皮脂線可唔可以做手術切左佢 好似汗腺個類咁<br />\n<br />\n唔該求解答"},{"pid":"fdcffa0e4232614b0a0d418d8038359818f6de5a","tid":542482,"uid":26156,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T13:42:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"32b21abffbde1abce1314f721ba5e217c8138ddd","tid":542482,"uid":15501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T13:49:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5aeda3dda6bf658b29dffaa3e7b2c527c916f119","tid":542482,"uid":137731,"like":3,"dislike":11,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T13:54:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0bc8a1a22a38a98b2fa585957d09cc2209ed2ac4","tid":542482,"uid":15501,"like":4,"dislike":9,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"5aeda3dda6bf658b29dffaa3e7b2c527c916f119","tid":542482,"uid":137731,"like":3,"dislike":11,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T13:54:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T13:57:26.000Z","msg":"收皮啦 屌你老母"},{"pid":"b96785dc8cb5e09614a70cd6a4ae42a01f115ecc","tid":542482,"uid":45772,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"0bc8a1a22a38a98b2fa585957d09cc2209ed2ac4","tid":542482,"uid":15501,"like":4,"dislike":9,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"5aeda3dda6bf658b29dffaa3e7b2c527c916f119","tid":542482,"uid":137731,"like":3,"dislike":11,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T13:54:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T13:57:26.000Z","msg":"收皮啦 屌你老母"}